We need to extract the following two items:

1. The cost incurred in securing customer orders and delivering goods and services. In our statements this cost appears as the Selling Expenses in the Income Statement.
2. The cash payments to acquire property, plant and equipment and other long-term assets. In our statements this is shown as Purchase of Fixed Assets in the Cash Flow Statement (under Investing Activities).

Looking at the provided Income Statement:
• Selling Expenses is reported as 1325774.90

Looking at the provided Cash Flow Statement:
• Purchase of Fixed Assets is reported as 2670827.47

Thus the solution is as follows:
